{"tid":237355,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE History] 歷史科討論區","createTime":"2017-05-10T10:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T10:43:30.000Z","uid":83903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85a233b77716ca820ce5cc06a86e0ea6b9a4c4e6","tid":237355,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"上個post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/131814/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/131814/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟兩三年前已經係網上分享歷史科既免費資源比應考既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開post除左諗住等多D 巴絲可以接觸到免費資源可以作為補充之外<br />\n都想有個平台大家討論下<br />\n<br />\n有卷想我幫手改既都可以send email比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\njohnnymahistory@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n其他免費資源可以上FB睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dsehistoryjohnnymahistory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdsehistoryjohnnymahistory%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=6d11fcfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dsehistoryjohnnymahistory/</a>"},{"pid":"4cd1f838971c1644305cbdbb4278ca5b9ad0868c","tid":237355,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"我諗大家都知History考試分ESSAY同DBQ啦<br />\n咁我先分享小小ESSAY既野比巴絲先<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1. ESSAY</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nESSAY唯一同以往唔同既係2018年開始轉左25分一題 因為取消左SBA<br />\n但係時間就冇變到 都係90分鍾做兩題 即係45分鍾一題<br />\n<br />\n我諗最多人擔心既應該係下面兩個問題:<br />\n1. 究竟以前同E家既評分準則有冇變到呢?<br />\n考評局話冇<br />\n<br />\n2. 以前既分數 (15分滿分) 同E家既分數點樣比較?<br />\n大家可以上返下面考評局網站到睇返個分數既變化<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Subject_Information/hist/hist-MarkScale2018-C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FSubject_Information%2Fhist%2Fhist-MarkScale2018-C.pdf&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=7d6ac56d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Subject_Information/hist/hist-MarkScale2018-C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n例如以往既14-15分即係E家既23-25分等等...."},{"pid":"74499e3b8bf7a7de7db632737e19cc4296af2641","tid":237355,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"ESSAY既出題模式大致同下面相若:<br />\n<br />\nQ1-Q3會出亞洲史 (Theme A)<br />\n如果唔出東南亞咁一定係香港﹑日本同中國<br />\n<br />\nQ4-Q6會出歐洲史 (Theme B)<br />\n正常黎講兩次大戰 (Two world wars), 冷戰 (Cold War) &amp; 歐洲經濟統合 (European economic integration)<br />\n冷門既話係國際協作 (International cooperation) 或者二戰後主要衝突 (Major conflicts after WWII) 個三個Topic<br />\n<br />\nQ7會係開放題目 (多通簡一個國家/地區 country/ region, 但2016出左簡一個禍害 select one disaster in your history course)<br />\n<br />\n正所以知己知彼 百戰百勝<br />\n溫書之前最緊要梗係知道考評局歷屆試題出過咩Topic同埋問過邊方面既題目<br />\n<br />\n我整左一張試題內容 (by topic) 既圖 (中文版)<br />\n希望幫到咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/2017ESSAY%20summary%20-1_zpsykwm5asu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2F2017ESSAY%2520summary%2520-1_zpsykwm5asu.jpg&h=4e51dfcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"776498f3d821a1917cc26b6a3ef97c412f072b4e","tid":237355,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"英文讀既巴打可以睇下面summarize既圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/2017%20ESSAY%20summary%20-1_zpstjkjehdg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2F2017%2520ESSAY%2520summary%2520-1_zpstjkjehdg.jpg&h=acaf738c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}